# Naming (new files)

Full pack: [docs/product/NAMING.md](docs/product/NAMING.md) · map: [ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/product/ARCHITECTURE.md) · [HYGIENE.md](docs/product/HYGIENE.md).

| Kind | Convention |
|------|------------|
| React components | `PascalCase.tsx` |
| Hooks / modules / mounts / contracts | `camelCase.ts(x)` |
| Screen folders | kebab **`=` `screenId`** (`book-step-1`, not `book-step1`) |
| Page / kit CSS | `kebab-case.css` (BEM block ≈ screenId) |
| PANEL chrome CSS | `.studio-nav-*` / `.studio-*` — **no new `.proto-*`** |
| DOM attrs | `data-studio-*` — **no new `data-proto-*`** |
| Product doctrine docs | `SCREAMING_SNAKE.md` |
| Project docs | `docs/projects/<id>/…` |
| Scripts | `kebab-case.mjs` |
| Tests | `*.test.ts` in `__tests__/` (colocated OK for tiny UXDS pure units) |

**Hard forbid:** no new `proto*` / `Proto*` filenames; no new `.proto-*` / `data-proto-*`. Prefer `window.__studio*`; keep `__proto*` aliases. Concept LEGACY `.proto-*` may remain until that Make screen retires.

**Forward-only:** do not mass-rename historical docs. High-ROI renames only when they stop agents stumbling.
